name: DisableUser2fa
description:
Disable two-factor authentication for a user.

This tool disables two-factor authentication (2FA) for a user and removes all associated devices. Use this when a user needs to deactivate their 2FA settings.

parameters.name: user_unique_identifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the user whose 2FA is to be disabled.

parameters.name: user_2fa_deactivation_details
parameters.description: JSON object with user details like uuid, email, 2FA status, and other relevant information required for deactivation.
